definitions.definition: A person who manufactures or shapes steel .
examples: The United Steelworkers strike closed the mill.

definitions.definition: A person employed to build steel structures, an ironworker .
examples: The steelworkers and electricians went on strike, halting construction.

main_definition: A person who manufactures or shapes steel .
secondary_definitions: ( uncommon ) A person employed to build steel structures, an ironworker .
